        "
        ``pmsx003,wake``

        ","
        Pulls the ``SET`` pin high, to wake the sensor.
        "
        "
        ``pmsx003,sleep``

        ","
        Pulls the ``SET`` pin low, so the sensor will go in sleep mode.
        "
        "
        ``pmsx003,reset``

        ","
        If the ``RST`` pin is set, the pin will be pulled down for 250 msec to reset the sensor.
        "
